data.description: 10.5 irrigated acres with 3 bedroom, 2 bath mobile home and sweeping views of the La Platas and San Juan Mountains. Complete utility hookups and expanded septic sysytem are ready for a new build or for parking your RV. Mobile home has addition with garage, covered porch, and laundry/mud room plus a fenced in yard for pets. Outside there is a spacious greenhouse and plenty of room for a big garden and all your animals. So many possibilities here! Diamond in the rough just 7 minutes to Ignacio and 20 minutes to Durango.
